{"tid":1568292,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"大家唔好再爭論對與錯住， 入黎睇下天琦同大家點講","createTime":"2019-09-14T09:08:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T09:24:23.000Z","uid":29581,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"76548adb844963e3e8269fc92e6c754178d4701e","tid":1568292,"uid":29581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:08:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地依個社會，要攞番應有嘅權力，唔可以繼續教條主義，條條大路通羅馬，邊個方式可以推翻政府，邊個方式就應該去做。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">相信和平抗爭嘅人、相信公民抗命嘅人，繼續公民抗命；相信佔馬路、相信絕食、相信罷交稅等等和平手段，繼續去做。我鼓勵你地去做，我希望你地去做。我唔希望因為有人批評你地嘅手段，結果就完全放棄你地相信嘅嘢。<br />\n同時間，相信勇武抗爭嘅人，一樣要繼續做</span></span>"},{"pid":"5dd900d1947c9e6b40b85c1ae260743a0dcaa4a7","tid":1568292,"uid":29581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:10:19.000Z","msg":"/<br />\n1/10"},{"pid":"85b636dee2880a57a87d172508d562fb8bbd03c8","tid":1568292,"uid":29581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:10:29.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"b44d1a64b1eacd2a33ae43ca56d215683e8fedc8","tid":1568292,"uid":29581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:10:42.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"234f613e46d560db7685676b493fa51798bf542e","tid":1568292,"uid":29581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:11:36.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"1adc7fbc93b65c425bdfa913aa71c5affde52e13","tid":1568292,"uid":9103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:11:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>［求推］請記住我地最大既武器其實係團結<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568082\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568082</a></blockquote><br />\n兄弟爬山，各自努力<br />\n不分化不割蓆不篤灰"},{"pid":"7004cb78399e28adc04af60c9c9d923729e6b1e8","tid":1568292,"uid":192893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:12:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/@.gif\" class=\"hkgm